data.description:
Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough

Nestled in the heart of Castle Rock, Colorado, this gorgeous home at 1198 Atkinson Ave offers the epitome of suburban living. Boasting four generously sized bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this residence caters effortlessly to modern family life. Upon entering, guests are greeted by the grand ambiance of a fireplace in the spacious living room, perfect for relaxing evenings or entertaining guests.

The allure of this property extends beyond its interior, with a large backyard providing ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings. Whether it's hosting summer barbecues or enjoying a quiet morning coffee, this backyard oasis offers endless possibilities for enjoyment and relaxation.

For those seeking additional space, the basement provides a versatile area that can be customized to suit a variety of needs, from a home gym to a recreational area or additional storage space.

Convenience is key with an attached two-car garage, ensuring easy access and ample parking for vehicles or storage. Additionally, the home has been meticulously maintained, with attention to detail evident throughout, ensuring peace of mind for homeowners.

Located in a sought-after neighborhood in Castle Rock, residents will enjoy the tranquility of suburban living while still being within close proximity to local amenities, schools, parks, and recreational opportunities. With its spacious layout, desirable features, and prime location, 1198 Atkinson Ave presents an exceptional opportunity to own a slice of suburban paradise in one of Colorado's most desirable communities.
